headline: E&Ps Capitalize on AI Surge with NatGas Investments, But Volatility Expected
summary: EOG, Diamondback and Gulfport Energy remain optimistic—despite recent near-term volatility—and are doubling down on natural gas investments in order to meet growing energy demands.
